# PostHog (website analytics). Cookieless, no banner needed —
# see app/lib/analytics.ts for the strict-mode config.
# Project key from posthog.com → Project → Settings → API key.
VITE_POSTHOG_KEY=
# Optional. Defaults to https://us.i.posthog.com.
# Set to https://eu.i.posthog.com if your project is in the EU region.
VITE_POSTHOG_HOST=
